  "id": "RAW_aea7e8e0",
  "title": "「自然选择」融资 3000 万美元，阿里、蚂蚁布局 AI 陪伴",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzk0MDMyNDUxOQ==&mid=2247497250&idx=1&sn=4ba5d2e887af4f07914b528a888e2ca6",
  "date": "2026-01-20 00:55:00",
  "author": "暗涌Waves",
  "siteName": "暗涌Waves",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"2 3 []\" style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"960\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/BhIKFZ2E88hSV5Qv37LZ3MSc2rQIjaMuHV2BLpxp8RWrIKpqQZp6ck1bPfHbwE1MHP5b5JGz3FBic55kt8YnMmw/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"100013586\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7b75fadf&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FBhIKFZ2E88hSV5Qv37LZ3MSc2rQIjaMuHV2BLpxp8RWrIKpqQZp6ck1bPfHbwE1MHP5b5JGz3FBic55kt8YnMmw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-top: 24px;margin-bottom: 48px;text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 175, 0);\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">「</span></strong></span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">虚拟陪伴走向真实世界。</span></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 175, 0);\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">」</span></strong></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: right;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">文</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);\"><span leaf=\"\">｜</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">施嘉翔</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: right;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.12444444444444444\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"900\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"72\" data-imgfileid=\"100011910\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2d912896&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FBhIKFZ2E88gzESQ19UqrtSgjbbIfXapAPVuIicnkFMjZ2m7IPq7oVSPKaK9lLSh3y154FrDKasnyaqiaKd9yF90A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif\"></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">「暗涌Waves」独家获悉，AI陪伴公司「自然选择」（Nature Select）已于近期完成新一轮融资，金额超3000万美元。本轮融资由阿里巴巴、蚂蚁集团、启明创投、五源资本、创世伙伴创投、云时资本等机构联合投资。星涵资本为本轮独家财务顾问。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">AI陪伴赛道在2025年上半年一度遇冷，C.ai类产品被认为“增长天花板低、长留差、且很难商业化”。而「自然选择」推出的《EVE》在年中首测，向整个业界呈现了一个全新的AI陪伴产品形态。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">他们对“AI陪伴”做了五个维度上的重新定义——</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">1.&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">Proactive（主动发起）：拒绝被动响应，具备独立意志的主动关怀；</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">2.&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">双商兼具的“活人感”：用Agent的方式做对话，同时拥有高情商与高智商，脱离“人机感”；</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">3.&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">SOTA 级长时记忆：记住细节与脉络，更符合人类直觉的回忆与遗忘机制；</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">4.&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">高沉浸感：引入3D视觉与游戏化设计，极大提升沉浸代入感；</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 175, 0);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">5.&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">破次元Agent：打通生活服务，真正介入和便利用户的现实生活。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">以破次元Agent为例，EVE用户在达到一定亲密度后，AI男友会给玩家点奶茶。这一“破次元壁”的操作曾广泛出圈。据「暗涌Waves」了解，这类打破虚拟与现实边界的体验，或许是阿里等投资方共同入局的原因之一。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">另据了解，「自然选择」通过设置名为“情感交互设计师”的职位来提高AI的情商。他们还在今年发布了首个情感大模型Echo-N1，提出一套全新的“情感模型训练方法”，以及专门用来衡量情商的benchmark，首次将RL用在了主观情感领域。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">“我们越来越发现，情商的本质可能就是智商。”创始人Tristan曾这样说。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 24px 16px 0px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"348\" data-backw=\"370\" data-imgfileid=\"100013595\" data-ratio=\"0.9405405405405406\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"370\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9d2b2f16&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2FBhIKFZ2E88iatV6T9frUKJKBgngUeib58dB6c8vzSCquE0dTRJQ6oKl8ygyIdFlRXpovXbicseyzzG7ribbvh7Y1RA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: right;margin: 0px 16px;line-height: 1em;\"><span data-pm-slice=\"2 3 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: right;margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: right;margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;2 3 [\\&quot;para\\&quot;,{\\&quot;tagName\\&quot;:\\&quot;p\\&quot;,\\&quot;attributes\\&quot;:{\\&quot;style\\&quot;:\\&quot;text-align: right;margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1em;\\&quot;},\\&quot;namespaceURI\\&quot;:\\&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\\&quot;}]&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">图片来源：EVE PV</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">在EVE首测后被持续加强的还有记忆系统。早在2024年，「自然选择」团队就提出了128个动态记忆槽位的长时记忆方案，到2025年又给记忆系统加入了多维graphRAG。Tristan曾告诉「暗涌Waves」，“记忆系统的本质是推荐系统”，而他们在按照搜推的方式做记忆。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">启明创投合伙人王世雨告诉「暗涌Waves」，其投资「自然选择」的主要原因是，「自然选择」通过主动Agent的交互范式，构建一种“自然积累用户的context和memory，并与游戏化设计深层次融合的全新交互体验”；云时资本投资人孙宇光在Tristan创业初期就与他相识。他告诉「暗涌Waves」，自己看好「自然选择」的原因是，Tristan把时间和精力花在了真正能产生壁垒的事情身上：3D和数据。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">2025年中以来，AI陪伴赛道愈发拥挤，而「自然选择」目前看来呈现的核心优势在于：既为AI公司，有完整的post-training团队和长期记忆之类的专家系统；也有游戏公司背景，能做3D视觉和恋爱游戏化设计。但每个人类个体对于情感都有不尽相同的需求，这场瞄准“最人类”部分的AI商业大战，也只是刚刚开始。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">Tristan曾对「暗涌Waves」说，EVE是他必然通向的路，而「自然选择」的终极目标是——</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 24px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">“</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.6em;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">迎接硅基生命降临，并创造一个人与AI共存的世界。”</span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "AI 陪伴公司「自然选择」获 3000 万美元融资，通过主动交互、情感大模型及破次元服务重新定义虚拟陪伴。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "AI 陪伴公司「自然选择」获 3000 万美元融资，通过主动交互、情感大模型及破次元服务重新定义虚拟陪伴。",
  "summary": "本文报道了 AI 陪伴初创公司「自然选择」（Nature Select）完成由阿里、蚂蚁领投的新一轮 3000 万美元融资。文章重点介绍了其产品《EVE》如何通过五个维度重新定义 AI 陪伴：主动发起交互、双商兼具的活人感、SOTA 级长时记忆、3D 游戏化沉浸感以及打通现实生活服务的“破次元”能力。技术层面，公司发布了情感大模型 Echo-N1，并利用 GraphRAG 和搜推逻辑构建记忆系统，试图打破 C.ai 类产品增长乏力的困局，实现虚拟与现实的深度融合。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "「自然选择」通过五个维度重新定义 AI 陪伴，核心在于主动性与破次元能力。",
      "explanation": "产品不再是被动响应，而是具备独立意志的主动关怀，并能通过打通生活服务（如点奶茶）介入用户现实生活。"
    },
    {
      "point": "公司发布首个情感大模型 Echo-N1，将强化学习应用于主观情感领域。",
      "explanation": "通过设置情感交互设计师职位和专门的 EQ benchmark，利用 RL 提升 AI 的情商，认为情商本质上是智商的体现。"
    },
    {
      "point": "采用搜推逻辑和多维 GraphRAG 构建 SOTA 级长时记忆系统。",
      "explanation": "记忆系统被视为推荐系统，通过 128 个动态记忆槽位和图检索增强技术，使 AI 具备符合人类直觉的遗忘与回忆机制。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "虚拟陪伴走向真实世界。",
    "我们越来越发现，情商的本质可能就是智商。",
    "记忆系统的本质是推荐系统，而他们在按照搜推的方式做记忆。",
    "迎接硅基生命降临，并创造一个人与 AI 共存的世界。"
  ],
  "tags": [
    "AI 陪伴",
    "情感大模型",
    "Agent",
    "自然选择",
